OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781549299
OL,3,CSoaring temperatures from Spain and
OL,4,CPortugal could reach UK this weekend
OL,6,FDespite some rays of sunshine over the
OL,7,Fweekend, it has been a far-from
OL,8,Fsummery feel to June so far.
OL,10,FHowever, this is set to change as
OL,11,Fsoaring temperatures across Spain,
OL,12,FPortugal, and France could push UK
OL,13,Ftemperatures towards 30C this weekend.
OL,15,FSo how hot will it get, and what can
OL,16,Fwe expect in the coming days?
OL,18,FWhen is summer set to return?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
