FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781549299
OL,3,CSoaring temperatures from Spain and
OL,4,CPortugal could reach UK this weekend
OL,6,FDespite warm weather coming our way,
OL,7,Fit will take a bit longer for a
OL,8,Fsignificant improvement to last week's
OL,9,Funseasonably cool and rainy conditions.
OL,11,FLow-pressure systems in the Atlantic
OL,12,Fwill continue to bring fresh and cool
OL,13,Fconditions for this time of year.
OL,15,FMore wet weather will arrive from the
OL,16,Fwest on Tuesday and Wednesday,
OL,17,Faccompanied by blustery winds as the
OL,18,Frain moves through.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
