PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781549299
OL,3,CSoaring temperatures from Spain and
OL,4,CPortugal could reach UK this weekend
OL,6,FBut warmer air from Europe will try to
OL,7,Fnudge into the southern parts of
OL,8,FEngland - making it feel milder.
OL,10,FHigher pressure will try to edge in
OL,11,Ffrom the south and south-west as the
OL,12,Fweek continues, which indicates hints
OL,13,Fof temperatures starting to recover
OL,14,Fand jump up a few degrees.
OL,16,FWhat temperatures can we expect?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781549299
OL,3,CSoaring temperatures from Spain and
OL,4,CPortugal could reach UK this weekend
OL,6,FWith high pressure encouraging drier
OL,7,Fand settled conditions across the
OL,8,Fsouth - plus more June sunshine - it
OL,9,Fwon't take much for temperatures to
OL,10,Frise.
OL,12,FBy the end of the week, it'll feel
OL,13,Fmuch warmer for many, with potential
OL,14,Fhighs of 28-30C or more currently
OL,15,Fforecast for the south-east and
OL,16,Feastern areas.
OL,18,FThese areas are most likely to see the
OL,19,Fhighest temperatures as heat builds
OL,20,Facross Europe in the next few days.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
