FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781549299
OL,3,CSoaring temperatures from Spain and
OL,4,CPortugal could reach UK this weekend
OL,6,FIt'll become hotter across most of the
OL,7,Fcontinent by the end of the week, with
OL,8,Ftemperatures soaring across Spain,
OL,9,FPortugal, and France.
OL,11,FThis heat has a chance of gradually
OL,12,Finfluencing our warmth into Thursday,
OL,13,FFriday, and the following weekend.
OL,15,FWill it be sunny and warm everywhere?
OL,17,FAt this stage, in the coming days,
OL,18,Fthere's a split in our weather pattern
OL,19,Fbetween the southeast and northwest.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
