PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781549299
OL,3,CSoaring temperatures from Spain and
OL,4,CPortugal could reach UK this weekend
OL,6,FThere's more of a focus on sunny and
OL,7,Fwarmer conditions further south and
OL,8,Feast - so these areas are most likely
OL,9,Fto feel hotter by the end of the week.
OL,11,FThe north and north-west will remain
OL,12,Fmore exposed to fresher air from the
OL,13,FAtlantic and weather systems that
OL,14,Fbring further outbreaks of rain and
OL,15,Fbreezy winds.
OL,17,FWhere sunshine develops in sheltered
OL,18,Fspots, it will be a welcome respite.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
