PN,31407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781549299
OL,3,CSoaring temperatures from Spain and
OL,4,CPortugal could reach UK this weekend
OL,6,FWith the Summer Solstice next weekend,
OL,7,Fdays are at their longest this time of
OL,8,Fyear, so there's always time for
OL,9,Fdrier, brighter conditions to develop.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/7
